{"tid":1303904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴正呼籲】袁澧淋被沙狗中出至大肚／屌雙穴／抱起嚟屌等言論　應該立即停止！","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T18:02:32.000Z","uid":14328,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3069fdc7c345034f6a14052917406256cc432f","tid":1303904,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/0zOmiST.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zOmiST.gif&h=ddf39c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年佢地兩個拍拖，一個未知人會做狗，一個未知人會做明星，乾柴烈火同住一室，就算有做愛，喺年青人間，係極為平常之事。<br />\n<br />\n為免失去中間派／女性支持，連登仔應停止狙擊！任何有關佢被沙狗中出至大肚，抱起嚟屌，係宿舍做愛，屌屎眼，爽到反白眼，玩左好多招式，等相關言論，應該立即停止！<br />\n<br />\n而且希望大家如要評論，應該就事實而作出見解，比如當年沙狗仲未獲頒「榮譽警棍」，袁澧淋係果一個時間點，係無可能一邊比沙狗屌屎忽，一邊比佢用榮譽警棍插，使出「玩雙穴」等招式。<br />\n<br />\n而且此等下流評論，實在有失禮儀，不應由現時形象高質嘅抗爭者口中所說，希望大家可以忍忍口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3f1ca732408327d9ebd9dc0d2c6f4c053ceceb","tid":1303904,"uid":219398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"笑撚死我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c85b9cc8478d4c9c1c508c2003b76293e0dcce","tid":1303904,"uid":53133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"唔該你唔好拉去我地香港抗爭到做藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請問沙sir嘅所作所為唔通我地作為高質抗爭者就要覺得佢岩？"},{"pid":"1ef8ea4c061f87009942b1cc9d558bee0b805363","tid":1303904,"uid":158301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3c85b9cc8478d4c9c1c508c2003b76293e0dcce","tid":1303904,"uid":53133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,